## 1. Role Of This File

When a {{EXPERIMENT_UNIT_LABEL}} produces metrics, record them here first, then cascade the verdict (not the raw numbers) to `docs/project/project-status.md` and the index in `docs/project/themes/theme-index.md`. The discipline: numbers live here once; prose elsewhere refers to them by {{EXPERIMENT_UNIT_LABEL}} id. This keeps one editable copy, so a correction never has to be chased across files.

